{"tid":2079774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一個月發兩次盈警 富臨翠華最新虧損較前高逾倍","createTime":"2020-06-26T04:19:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T05:39:33.000Z","uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fdce62a73bbded27bb7ab6cfdd0c653995742a1b","tid":2079774,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T04:19:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://statics.exmoo.com/uploads/2020-06-26/bqzsdfIX4lA0s0sKlPpO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatics.exmoo.com%2Fuploads%2F2020-06-26%2FbqzsdfIX4lA0s0sKlPpO.jpg&h=44ad297b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有甚麼較發一次盈警痛苦？答案係發兩次盈警。雖然餐飲股早前已預告會虧損，但到今天，上市企業發覺虧損較想像中來得要大，於是再度敲響警鐘。富臨集團（1443）及翠華（1314）更新公告，截至今年3月底止虧損較早前預計要高，分別增2倍及1倍。<br />\n<br />\n零售業同樣不好過，優品360（2360）公布全年業績，截至今年3月底止，純利為1,210萬元，按年大減79.7%；每股盈利1.2仙，不派末期息。期內，收入跌4.5%，至12.3億元。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.exmoo.com/article/151928.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"6f9ae7578f0fb474fc391fa397d2525460f8fc8e","tid":2079774,"uid":52087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T04:27:54.000Z","msg":"快撚啲執柒左佢"},{"pid":"d42f790c4f55e4ee586fb55cfe3dd4f11f5cb883","tid":2079774,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T04:59:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a25ee1aecd8817d52fcae342de031aac55a1f260","tid":2079774,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T05:00:14.000Z","msg":"政府會唔會注資?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f906e4db443656b3ac7960727e21d15d0fb27ee7","tid":2079774,"uid":73569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T05:01:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ddaff7f904caff1cc509259295228e0e968c977","tid":2079774,"uid":108560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T05:02:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=